      "content": "thanks. i get that they were racist, but for the debate i really need to simulate the actual logic they used to make it sound reasonable to people back then. like, can you expand on the \"community stability\" argument? can you give me some more specific, structured points on how they linked segregation to economic security or urban planning efficiency? i need to be able to present their side convincingly so my opponent doesn't catch me off guard.",
